text: Pyotr Petrovich Stepanov (; born 2 January 1959) is a Transnistrian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Transnistria from 18 January 2012 until 10 July 2013.Kyiv Post - Pyotr Stepanov becomes head of Transdniestrian Cabinet ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Transnistria
